snippet: Promoted RB Leipzig will look to complete a sensational year with victory at champions Bayern Munich on Wednesday as they eye top spot in the Bundesliga going into the winter break....
lead_paragraph: Promoted RB Leipzig will look to complete a sensational year with victory at champions Bayern Munich on Wednesday as they eye top spot in the Bundesliga going into the winter break.

headline.main: Leipzig Out to Cap Sensational Year With Win at Bayern
headline.print_headline: Leipzig Out to Cap Sensational Year With Win at Bayern
